x=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Class Balance = EZ</span><hr size=1> Yes, I deffinitly think it should be done. Mostly because its an uppgrade that doesnt stack with getting mana buffs of others as much as improved mana ratio of spells. Of course, both needs to be done, but it will make it easier to upgrade wizards for groups without making wizards raid gods. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaiyanenfarre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aiyane N Farre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/12/02 10:12:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=712.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://mywebpages.comcast.net/jeffreywarner/Images/Aiyane2.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Class Balance = EZ</span><hr size=1> Ummm, just so you know.....<br><br>It already scales with level, it gives 5 * lvl mana. Most people think it doesn't scale enough though. Personally I would just like them to reduce the recast to 5 minutes.<br><br>On the other hand if they keep going with the caster balance and add real focus items soon it may not be needed.<br><br>Fixing our familiar so we can actually use it again would help too. 60 familar + harvest works out to 7 mana/tick = Clarity.<br> <p>Aiyane N'Farre<BR>Pyrotechnic<BR><a target="new" href="http://www.ilsikhaucil.com/">Ilsik Haucil</a><BR><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=133769">My Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=712.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nb